‚Ä¢ Continue refining the translation engines for speed and accuracy

Final Thoughts

This project taught me more than any class could.
It represents years of curiosity, trial and error, and persistence.

I don‚Äôt think I‚Äôll ever stop coding ‚Äî so follow HippoBot‚Äôs journey as it evolves over the years.
